      "cooked": "<p>Hi, I just updated the app before my workout but then found I can\u2019t use any of the modes that control the trainer. I can only use the base resistance level with power reported to the app. I\u2019ve tried turning Bluetooth on and off and also deleted and reinstalled the app. I\u2019m on ios, and my trainer is a Tacx vortex.</p>\n<p>See my screenshot and that the HR/ERG/slope mode is not selectable at all.</p>\n<p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://forums.trainerday.com/uploads/default/original/2X/e/e80aecf724006ed419b0721dce00210165a694c3.png\" data-download-href=\"https://forums.trainerday.com/uploads/default/e80aecf724006ed419b0721dce00210165a694c3\" title=\"IMG_4810\"><img src=\"https://forums.trainerday.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/e/e80aecf724006ed419b0721dce00210165a694c3_2_231x500.png\" alt=\"IMG_4810\" data-base62-sha1=\"x6KbeESxv3134zzcPQmvZ12abh9\" width=\"231\" height=\"500\" srcset=\"https://forums.trainerday.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/e/e80aecf724006ed419b0721dce00210165a694c3_2_231x500.png, https://forums.trainerday.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/e/e80aecf724006ed419b0721dce00210165a694c3_2_346x750.png 1.5x, https://forums.trainerday.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/e/e80aecf724006ed419b0721dce00210165a694c3_2_462x1000.png 2x\" data-small-upload=\"https://forums.trainerday.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/e/e80aecf724006ed419b0721dce00210165a694c3_2_10x10.png\"><div class=\"meta\"><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-far-image svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use xlink:href=\"#far-image\"></use></svg><span class=\"filename\">IMG_4810</span><span class=\"informations\">1170\u00d72532 159 KB</span><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-discourse-expand svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use xlink:href=\"#discourse-expand\"></use></svg></div></a></div> <div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://forums.trainerday.com/uploads/default/original/2X/7/7f96d00b13618a17a0ba8a8cb31cef7fe